Package veve.datastructures.trees

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NearestCommonAncestorTool<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>,​V>
    A tool used to find the nearest common ancestor between two NTreeNodes, the nodes from the first node to the ancestor, from the ancestor to the first node, the nodes from the second node to the ancestor, the nodes from the ancestor to the second node, the nodes from the first node to the second node passing through the ancestor and the nodes from the second node to the first node passing through the ancestor.
    NTree<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>,​V>
    A mutable tree composed of nodes where each node can have zero or any number of children.
    NTreeConstants  
    NTreeNode<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>,​V>
    A tree node that has an id, a value and zero or more child nodes.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    NTreeConstants.NodeValueCloningMode
    Used to determine the way the value property of a node is cloned.
    NTreeConstants.TreeTraversalOrder
    Used to determine the traversal order of the tree.
